snippet.textDisplay: The creepy thing about Judge Doom from Rodger Rabbit was he was loosely based on a Nazi judge who was known as Hitler's Hanging Judge (Roland Freisler I think was his name.) He was the one who sentenced the conspirators to death who tried to bomb Hitler and he had a hand at the Wansee Conference where the Holocaust was planned. The man had a horrifying screeching voice. His head was cracked open during an American bombing and he died.

The whole scene is just terrifying.
